text: Superb japan glass quality & after sales service! Returning customer to purchase cabinet with 6ft tank for a steal. Boss Dan was responsive to enquiries and willing to share knowledge. Highly recommended for fish-lovers!

Bad experience with Dan Lee, asked for quote for tank but he cannot give. Must visit him before he can give quote, experience is bad.

Not able to give quote not sure how i am able to purchase.
Great experience with Dan Lee! Very knowledgeable and professional!
Prompt in replies and follow up. A little on the pricey side hopefully quality are well matched.
